root: ^I better call the clinic to let them know I am to go.
^"Can you quickly check if the doctor is still in? "
^"He is. Are you coming to see him?"
^"No problem. We're located on Kirby Avenue, just in case you don't know already."
^"I am actually on Kirby Ave now."
^"Okay-- then just walk down it and we are right by the station."
